snippet: Seahawks quarterback Russell Wilson and his counterpart for the Chiefs, Alex Smith, struggled behind their unsettled offensive lines on Friday night in Kansas City’s 14-13 preseason victory.
abstract: NFL Roundup; Kansas City Chiefs defeat Seattle Seahawks, 14-13, in preseason game; other football news noted.
lead_paragraph: Seahawks quarterback Russell Wilson and his counterpart for the Chiefs, Alex Smith, struggled behind their unsettled offensive lines on Friday night in Kansas City’s 14-13 preseason victory.
